parameters.message: We start walking through corridors and more corridors.
"You'll get used to it. Look, there are the kitchens that we use on most classes."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: From the corridor that we are now, I can see a beautiful kitchen with long islands, each with a counter top stove.
Everything is so clean and shiny, so much better than what I had at home.
All the appliances and cooking utensils are like new, and I wonder how often they change everything there.
Suddenly, I realize Keisuke is not around anymore.
I think he was so focused on showing everything at the school that he didn't notice I stopped to admire this beautiful kitchen.
I decide to enter the kitchen to see everything from a closer distance.
I enter and there is a smell of Italian food. I look around and on one of the corners of the kitchen...
The most beautiful Lasagna I've ever seen. No. It's the most beautiful dish I've ever seen.
I never thought a italian dish could look so beautiful.
I feel a weird sensation in my pants. It's been a while since I felt aroused about anything.

parameters.button0Text: [OPT] I will stick my dick into it.
parameters.button1Text: [OPT] I will resist this weird urge.
